---
title: Speedy Mexican Fiesta Chicken Tacos with Mango Mayo & Coriander
description: Few things look as colourful as these tacos – with marinated chicken inside no less! The real star of this dish is the mayonnaise. There’s a hint of mango amidst the expected tang of mayonnaise we all know and love, and all of that means you’re in for a sweet ride.
